asset.hookText:
The Architecture Urban Collection successfully combines function with fashion, allowing modern professionals to move seamlessly from the working week into the weekend. True style is more than a look – it’s a way of life. This collection offers versatile designs, multi-purpose organization and multiple carrying options to ensure all your needs are met.

Each bag is expertly crafted using environmentally friendly Nüwa fabric and a traditional Napa-leather trim, resulting in a look that is casual yet refined. The collection’s smart design features are a reflection of the multi-functionality that is at the heart of the Victorinox brand.
